note over browser:
User clicks on the save button
end note

note over browser:
browser starts executing callback
code for submit button
end note

note over browser:
the browser stays on the same page, 
it sends no further HTTP requests
end note

browser->browser: Code redrawNotes()
browser->browser: Code sendToServer(note)


browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
server-->browser: [{"message":"note created"}]
